---

<section class="scene section" id="sticky">
  <div class="containnw">
    <div class="box1">
      <h1 class="bringheads">Explore Our Services</h1>
      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <div class="flex justify-center items-center mt-12 widhtimg">
          <img src={manmount.src} />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="box2 flex justify-center items-center">
      <div class="abc">
        <div class="flex flex-row justify-center">
          <div class="content text-center basis-3/4 sm:basis-1/3">
            <h1 class="digitall">Design</h1>
            <p class="repoeter">
              Step into a realm where colors dance and play, Where data takes on
              forms, in a whimsical display. Our artisans, skilled in the
              language of design, Craft a symphony of visuals that truly shine
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bluee">
        <div class="bbb flex items-center justify-center">
          <img src={news.src} class="imger" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="box1 flex justify-center items-center">
      <div class="abc">
        <div class="flex flex-row justify-center">
          <div class="content text-center basis-3/4 sm:basis-1/3">
            <h1 class="digitize">Digitize</h1>
            <p class="reports">
              From static to dynamic, reports come alive, A transformation that
              makes them thrive. With enchanting interactivity, they enchant and
              allure, Captivating audiences, experiences pure.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="green">
        <div class="bbb flex items-center justify-center">
          <img src={computer.src} class="img" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="box2 flex justify-center items-center">
      <div class="abc">
        <div class="flex flex-row justify-center">
          <div class="content text-center basis-3/4 sm:basis-1/3">
            <h1 class="digitall">Animate</h1>
            <p class="repoeter">
              A new dimension of interactivity we bring,  Engaging narratives,
              like a song to sing. Memorable moments, easy to comprehend,  With
              animation's magic, reports transcend.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bluee">
        <div class="bca flex items-center justify-center">
          <img src={Animate.src} class="imger" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="box1 flex justify-center items-center">
        <div class="abc">
          <div class="flex flex-row justify-center">
            <div class="content text-center basis-3/4 sm:basis-1/3">
              <h1 class="digitize">Report writing</h1>
              <p class="reports">
                Informative whispers, we weave with care, Speaking to your
                market, a message rare. Standing out from the crowd, with words
                that shine, Expertly written, a report so divine.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="green">
          <div class="bbb flex items-center justify-center">
            <div>
              <img src={handdroup.src} class="imge" />

              <div class="butt">
                <img src={buttonf.src} class="imggs" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="panell flex justify-center items-end">
        <h1 class="portfolio">Port &nbsp; olio</h1>
